Why use it at all if it's possible to instruct app to bind 0 and read the allocated port when needed? That fixture unbinds from port, meaning it might be intercepted by smth else as a result of race condition.
I'd go for `SO_REUSEPORT` or socket activation in order to make it more reliable.

